<li>Gastric and duodenal ulcers<sup id="cite_ref-Moerman_2000_72-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Moerman_2000-72" title=""><span>[</span>73<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-144" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-144" title=""><span>[</span>145<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Moerman_book_118-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Moerman_book-118" title=""><span>[</span>119<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
