<li>Herpes simplex<sup id="cite_ref-147" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-147" title=""><span>[</span>148<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Hypertension: mild and moderate<sup id="cite_ref-148" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-148" title=""><span>[</span>149<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Grenfell_20-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Grenfell-20" title=""><span>[</span>21<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Irritable bowel syndrome<sup id="cite_ref-149" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-149" title=""><span>[</span>150<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-150" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-150" title=""><span>[</span>151<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
