<li>Nausea and vomiting: postoperative (sham acupuncture)<sup id="cite_ref-155" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-155" title=""><span>[</span>156<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="margin-right: 20px;">
<ul>
<li>Pain<sup id="cite_ref-156" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-156" title=""><span>[</span>157<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-157" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-157" title=""><span>[</span>158<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Panic disorders<sup id="cite_ref-158" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-158" title=""><span>[</span>159<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Parkinson’s disease<sup id="cite_ref-159" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-159" title=""><span>[</span>160<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-160" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-160" title=""><span>[</span>161<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
