<li id="cite_note-119"><b><a href="#cite_ref-119" title="">^</a></b> In many of these citations concern research that show active treatments are effective. The point is that they also show placebo effects exist as well. It should not therefor be inferred that effective treatment in these conditions do not exist, only that placebo effects have been shown.</li>
