<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Placebo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=37" title="Edit section: History of medicine">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History of medicine</span></h3>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;-moz-column-count:2; -webkit-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ul>
<li>Anonymous, "The Bottle of Medicine" [Editorial], <i>British Medical Journal</i>, No.4750, (19 January 1952), pp.149–150. <i>Estimates that 40% of general practice patients receive a bottle of medicine as a placebo.</i></li>
<li>Ayad, H., "Khellin in Angina Pectoris", <i>The Lancet</i>, Vol.251, No.6495, (21 February 1948), Page 305.</li>
