<li>Evans, W. &amp; Hoyle, C., "The Comparative Value of Drugs Used in the Continuous Treatment of Angina Pectoris", <i>Quarterly Journal of Medicine</i>, No.7 (Vol.2, No.4), (July 1933), pp.311–338.</li>
