<p><a name="General_audience" id="General_audience"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Placebo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=39" title="Edit section: General audience">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">General audience</span></h3>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;-moz-column-count:2; -webkit-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ul>
<li>Brooks, Michael. <i>New Scientist Space.</i> March 19, 2005. <a href="http://www.newscientistspace.com/article.ns?id=mg18524911.600" class="external text" title="http://www.newscientistspace.com/article.ns?id=mg18524911.600" rel="nofollow">13 Things that do not make sense.</a> URL accessed April 25, 2008.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFDodes.2C_John_E">Dodes, John E (January/February 1997). <a href="http://www.csicop.org/si/9701/placebo.html" class="external text" title="http://www.csicop.org/si/9701/placebo.html" rel="nofollow">"The Mysterious Placebo"</a>. Skeptical Inquirer<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.csicop.org/si/9701/placebo.html" class="external free" title="http://www.csicop.org/si/9701/placebo.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.csicop.org/si/9701/placebo.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-05-08</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mysterious+Placebo&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Dodes%2C+John+E&amp;rft.au=Dodes%2C+John+E&amp;rft.date=January%2FFebruary+1997&amp;rft.pub=Skeptical+Inquirer&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csicop.org%2Fsi%2F9701%2Fplacebo.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Placebo"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> An overview of the placebo effect and how it influences the study of alternative medicines.</li>
