<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMcQuayMoore.2C_R._A.2009">McQuay, H. J.; Moore, R. A. (2005). "Placebo". <i>Postgraduate Medical Journal</i> <b>81</b>: 155–60. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fpgmj.2004.024737" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fpgmj.2004.024737" rel="nofollow">10.1136/pgmj.2004.024737</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15749790" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15749790">PMID 15749790</a> <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fpgmj.2004.024737" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fpgmj.2004.024737" rel="nofollow">10.1136/pgmj.2004.024737</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Placebo&amp;rft.jtitle=Postgraduate+Medical+Journal&amp;rft.aulast=McQuay&amp;rft.aufirst=H.+J.&amp;rft.au=McQuay%2C+H.+J.&amp;rft.au=Moore%2C+R.+A.&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.volume=81&amp;rft.pages=155%E2%80%9360&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1136%2Fpgmj.2004.024737&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/15749790+%5B%5BDigital+object+identifier%7Cdoi%5D%5D%3A%5Bhttp%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1136%252Fpgmj.2004.024737+%7FUNIQ7e7b5fa31e6e29ec-nowiki-0000046C-QINU%7F%5D&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Placebo"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFMayo_Clinic">Mayo Clinic (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2003-12-31"><a href="/wiki/2003" title="2003">2003</a>-<a href="/wiki/December_31" title="December 31">12-31</a></span>). "<a href="http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2003/12/031231084101.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2003/12/031231084101.htm" rel="nofollow">Placebo effect: Harnessing your mind's power to heal</a>". <i>ScienceDaily</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2003/12/031231084101.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2003/12/031231084101.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2003/12/031231084101.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-04-26</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Placebo+effect%3A+Harnessing+your+mind%27s+power+to+heal&amp;rft.jtitle=ScienceDaily&amp;rft.aulast=Mayo+Clinic&amp;rft.au=Mayo+Clinic&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2003-12-31%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedaily.com%C2%AD%2Freleases%2F2003%2F12%2F031231084101.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Placebo"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
